ast - package ast
 
AST - Class in ast
The AST Abstract class is the Abstract Syntax Tree representation; each node contains references to its kids, its unique node number used for printing/debugging, its decoration used for constraining and code generation, and a label for code generation The AST is built by the Parser
AST() - Constructor for class ast.AST
 
ASTVisitor - Class in visitor
ASTVisitor class is the root of the Visitor hierarchy for visiting various AST's; each visitor asks each node in the AST it is given to accept its visit;
each subclass must provide all of the visitors mentioned in this class;
after visiting a tree the visitor can return any Object of interest
